Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:41.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99996,101080}Your attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101331,104959}This plane will be landing\Nwithin 20 minutes…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105084,107545}…at the New Tokyo\NInternational Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111382,113176}Who's that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113885,116554}Tomoko Nagata,\Nshe's 28 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116679,118681}A successful\Ndetective in the U. S.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119390,121434}She's so good\Nthat she solved a case…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121559,123061}…which even\Nthe FBI couldn't solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124437,127523}So why do we\Nhave to meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128066,130318}The mayor himself\Ninvited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130610,132695}This means you may\Nfinally lose your job…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133154,134739}…investigating St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138576,140328}She must be a very\Nold-fashioned, homely…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140453,141913}…and unpleasant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142288,144290}I'm sorry that I'm\Nan unpleasant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:42.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157720,162517}PHANTASMAL MASTERPIECE!\NA WOMAN DETECTIVE IS BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163101,164227}Do you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164352,166187}…about the mysterious\Nthief St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166813,168731}She uses magic freely…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169190,171651}…and she sends\Na warning note prior to her crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:54.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171859,174904}No one knows her identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:55.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175029,175988}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:57.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176155,177115}Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177240,178825}Then we can talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178950,180827}I want to ask you\Nfor your assistance…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180993,182370}…in catching St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183037,186874}I've assured you\Nthat I'll catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:12.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187125,192088}Yes. I expect you\Ncan catch her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193673,195717}But in this case…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195842,198761}…I think it's better\Nto ask this lovely lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201222,202390}I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202765,205643}…but I came back to Japan\Non a personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206018,207687}Can you make any\Narrangements to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207770,208771}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211858,213568}To-mo-ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215278,217071}I can give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217280,218906}I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219031,220491}…that I can't assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221826,223119}That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223453,226456}I definitely will\Narrest St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226664,228499}I'm the person\Nwho will catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228708,230960}Be quiet! This kind\Nof thing is done by age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231294,233713}That's unfair! All of a sudden\Nyou're motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:58.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234297,238760}Tomoko has sparked\Nthe detective fire in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239677,241137}It's nice to see a father\Nand son together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241637,243055}By the way, Asuka Jr. …
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243222,244807}…you go to St. Paulia's, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245099,246726}What? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247643,248770}Your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249312,251564}Say, could you show me\Naround the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252190,253191}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255860,258488}The graph for y=2x\Nis a straight line…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258613,260198}…which runs through the origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261824,263576}I wonder what\Nhappened to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264410,266662}He's healthy and has\Nnever missed any classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267622,269582}He was summoned\Nby the mayor…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269791,271334}…according to Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271542,273920}That means it must have\Nsomething to do with St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277089,278591}Hey, Asuka Jr. is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278716,280968}…walking with a really\Nbeautiful woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281302,282678}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284722,285973}She's really beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286182,288893}I didn't know that he\Nlikes older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290102,292271}What's going on?\NGo back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292396,294232}Oh, Nagata…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295149,296734}Do you know her, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297151,299570}Yes. She was\Nthe smartest student…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299654,301030}…in the history of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301155,302198}If I remember correctly…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302323,304325}…she went to a college in the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309330,310748}Do you know\Nabout her, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310832,312083}I've heard rumors about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312250,313751}She was the famous daughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313876,315169}…of a rich family in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315753,317672}On the hill from where\Nyou can see the port…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317880,319507}…there is a big\NEuropean-style house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319924,321509}You mean that\Nhaunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321843,324136}Yes. She used to live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324345,326597}But the people who\Nlived there are missing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:27.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326764,327807}…aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328182,330184}That's the rumor, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331060,334564}I've heard she's\Na famous detective now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334856,336607}What?! A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:47.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343865,347201}Just beyond here, I've found\Na really cute trinket store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347618,349203}Let's go, Meimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349662,351664}Yeah,\Nbut I have homework…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351789,353416}Just a little peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356210,357503}Oh, it's Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357712,359046}I wonder where she's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359297,360548}Let's follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360798,362300}What?! But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362425,364218}– Don't worry!\N– Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369473,370683}Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371684,373644}Isn't this\Nthe haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374312,375897}I've heard that a first-year\Nstudent in our school…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376022,378232}…heard a woman crying\Nin the middle of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378357,379317}Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387909,389243}We met earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389785,390912}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391621,393706}Tomoko Nagata.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394040,395833}Yes. I'm Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397501,399045}A delicate\Nand beautiful hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399670,401005}People who have\Nhands like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401172,402632}…are often magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405760,406802}Would you like to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406886,407929}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409764,410890}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:01.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418147,421442}A lot of my memories\Nare from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422318,425112}In your eyes, this must\Nbe like a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425529,426656}Oh, no…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426948,428616}They were\Nunderstanding parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429283,431327}When I said\NI wanted to study abroad…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431535,433287}…they let me do it\Nwithout saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:14.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433621,434580}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437249,438876}Let's go upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443589,445216}It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446509,448844}I was always dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449095,450930}From here…\Nfrom this window…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451847,453849}…I wanted to fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454266,455977}I wanted to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456477,458354}I didn't notice…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458521,460481}…my parents' love for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460940,463651}Your parents are…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:47.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,467029}Missing.\NSince I went abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468197,469156}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469240,471409}There's no reason\Nto tell you these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472326,473369}Please forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481836,482920}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483337,486090}I'm sorry\NI came in without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486298,487758}It brought back\Na lot of memories, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488300,489677}Please stay\Nas long as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490261,493389}To tell you the truth,\NI don't deserve to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:16.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494098,496684}Well, would you\Nlike to tell me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499520,500563}Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:21.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500855,501981}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502314,503733}The person\Nwho is responsible…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:24.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503816,504817}…for my parents'\Ndisappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505151,507528}I only came back here\Nto get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508112,511449}My parents were\Nart dealers in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:32.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511991,512992}Art dealers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513242,515995}Those people\Nwho sell pieces of art?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516370,517371}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524378,526547}My father was\Nstrict but affectionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526839,529383}Mother was always\Nwatching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530134,531802}I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532428,535056}The piece of art my parents\Ntreasured most was…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535514,537933}…a picture titled\N"Wings of Freedom."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538434,540394}But a man who wanted…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540519,542480}…"Wings of Freedom"\Nappeared one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543314,545441}Of course, my parents\Nturned down his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546859,549195}But in the end,\Nthey gave in to his enthusiasm…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549862,551155}…and they decided\Nto sell it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551739,554241}My father though that\Nhe would treasure the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554366,557411}But the man betrayed\Nmy father's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559121,561123}He said the picture\Nhe bought was a fake…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561290,563292}…and he sued my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563626,564627}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564960,567088}Because my father\Ndidn't have…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567171,568631}…any evidence\Nto prove otherwise…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568923,571383}…he had to pay a lot\Nof money and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572009,574970}Because of that he lost\Ncredibility as an art dealer…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575387,577014}…and he lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577306,578682}That's why they disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579391,581352}As I was abroad…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581936,583729}…I didn't know what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584105,585314}But I have always believed…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585439,587024}…that my parents were innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588818,591654}But in order to prove it…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592363,594115}…I didn't know what I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594198,595574}That's why you\Nbecame a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:59.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596784,599036}In order to become\Nstrong and take revenge…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599245,600996}…I endured the difficult training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606210,607169}I continued to investigate…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607419,608712}…the man who deceived…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608921,610214}…my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611423,612925}And the man is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614218,616220}He's the owner\Nof Sugawara Industries…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616303,617304}…Ryosuke Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618180,619974}She's going to steal?!\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620558,622434}If she can prove\Nthat Sugawara…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622643,625312}…has the real\N"Wings of Freedom"…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:28.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625855,628941}…then she can prove\Nher parents' innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629400,631986}No! She shouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632403,633487}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633737,635281}I'll steal the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635739,638325}I'll steal it\Nbefore Tomoko can…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638617,641078}…and reveal\NSugawara's crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641787,643831}Her revenge is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:45.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644498,645499}No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654800,658179}Today I'd like to take you around,\Naway from the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658554,659555}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661473,663642}I don't think you've seen enough\Nwith this boy as a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663809,666729}This time I'd like to show you\Nan adult's hospitality…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680951,682536}"I'm taking\N'Wings of Freedom'…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682661,684663}…that's in the possession\Nof Mr. Ryosuke Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:25.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684747,685748}– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686081,688292}– She is…!\N– What's that?
Comment: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:32.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:692713,692713}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:37.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:697718,697718}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697885,700846}The real "Wings of Freedom"\Nis in my possession?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:41.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700930,701972}Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702097,703098}You don't have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703682,704975}That's silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:48.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705184,708270}I've always wanted that piece…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:52.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708896,712107}Because of that,\NI once bought a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713984,716070}So you're saying\Nyou don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716362,718614}Of course I don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719114,722618}I'm the one who wants\Nto know where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724203,728249}I've heard of\Nthe mysterious thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728582,730501}She must have\Nmisunderstood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731126,732127}She is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:16.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732503,736173}It's not like St. Tail to send\Nan inaccurate warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736799,740177}You believe\Nthat petty thief's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740386,741971}She isn't a petty thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743806,745891}What Asuka Jr. said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746350,747601}According to my research…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747810,751772}…St. Tail has never sent\Nan inaccurate warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752189,753232}Not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:37.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753857,757111}If you let us search your house,\Nwe can clear this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757569,758529}I must refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759238,760197}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760614,762199}If you haven't done\Nanything wrong…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762366,763867}…it shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764326,765619}Because it isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765953,767079}You don't even\Nhave any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769707,771542}Chairman. It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772001,773002}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773419,774420}Detective Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774545,776046}I'll listen to your advice…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776213,777798}…and will let you\Nguard the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778090,779425}Then we'll do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780843,782970}Isn't she that\Nart dealer's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783429,785055}Yes. I had it confirmed…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785139,786890}…through an American\Ndetective agency…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786974,788225}…and there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788642,791145}Apparently she's been\Ninvestigating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791562,792563}This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792688,795107}If she finds out\NI have the real picture…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795316,796317}Then…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796692,798694}You don't even need to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798944,799903}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:26.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802948,806452}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811790,812916}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815336,816420}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:42.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818630,822301}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834229,836065}Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836231,838734}We don't know\Nwhat Tomoko will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839151,841278}Don't worry! It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843697,846950}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851580,853540}Asuka Jr., where is\NDetective Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853999,855667}He told me\Nhe had something…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855751,856794}…he needed to check…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857586,859880}What is he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875104,877439}I suppose she gave up…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880150,881860}Pretty impressive, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890744,893455}I can't let you interfere\Nwith my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897042,898043}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898127,899378}She's up in this tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899461,901171}Oh, no! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906677,907886}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908011,910139}Darn it! Never mind!\NLet's move in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910305,911265}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914435,915727}What shall I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921275,922609}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:31.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928157,931201}You saved me!\NThank you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960647,963233}This is the "Wings of Freedom"\Nyou were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963650,964610}The real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965444,967613}It's the one\Nyour father sold to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968030,970824}I prepared the counterfeit\Nand switched them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971700,973660}Now that you've seen the picture\Nyou were looking for…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973827,975913}…you don't have\Nany regrets, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976538,978040}The one who broke in\Nshould have been St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978207,979541}So, even if you disappear…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979708,982586}…no one will suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983629,984755}After the police leave…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984880,987799}…I'll decide how\Nyou should disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993096,995349}We've made the police leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995682,997601}But the media is making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998101,1001188}I guess it would be better\Nto give them an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001688,1002898}Let's have a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004733,1005692}This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010239,1011657}St. Tail…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015494,1016537}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016703,1018997}You know that I set you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028507,1029675}Oh, no…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030551,1032261}Let go! Let go of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032594,1033595}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034054,1035889}I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041144,1042896}You almost did it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043855,1044856}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:32.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051738,1052906}St. Tail…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053240,1055867}I'm sorry, but I can't\Ngive this picture to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:38.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057661,1058620}Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058870,1061582}You shouldn't steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061707,1062708}Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064751,1066753}Asuka Jr.!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067087,1068755}Over here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090777,1092070}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093280,1095365}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096325,1097909}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117220,1118430}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126104,1128231}A thief by the name of St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128482,1130609}…seems to have\Nbeen misinformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130859,1132778}Both six years ago and today…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132944,1134488}…I've been a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134863,1137783}You don't really have\N"Wings of Freedom," do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138158,1139242}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139493,1140827}If you have any doubt…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140911,1144373}…please go ahead and search\Nmy house or my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:13.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150420,1153507}That's a nice touch, Tajima…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156677,1159054}I, Ryosuke Sugawara,\Nswear to God…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159304,1161723}…that I am innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167020,1169690}It's the real\N"Wings of Freedom"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:34.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171650,1174528}– What?!\N– Please explain this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174611,1176738}I don't know!\NI don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177114,1178115}Mr. Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179282,1180909}Please come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182244,1184496}Have you discussed this\Nwith the mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184996,1186498}Maybe you should\Nhave a discussion…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:47.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186665,1187958}…with your conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189918,1192087}We've uncovered\Na few things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192921,1195132}The materials she\Ngave us helped a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195882,1198427}You'll have a lot of time\Nto tell us your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201346,1203765}Thank you, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206685,1208270}I heard that\NSugawara admitted…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208395,1210480}…deceiving your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211022,1212566}My dad was quite pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213150,1214443}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214776,1216820}Please thank your father for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217195,1218155}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219614,1220574}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237674,1238633}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239134,1240761}I'm cheering\Nfor you from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244514,1246057}What's the connection\Nbetween you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246600,1248435}We're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249352,1250729}I didn't know… Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251188,1253190}You don't understand.\NGuys don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253690,1255567}Wait! Hey, Meimi!
